Class DefaultSpaceState

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
Farmer, LectureSpaceState, MissionaryCannibal, TravelingSalesman, WaterJugs
public abstract class DefaultSpaceState
extends ImpObject
implements Searchable

Class DefaultSpaceState provides implementation of common behavior for Space states. It can not be instantiated, so application developers will need to extend it and implement extension specific method, here declared abstract
